snippet.title: A little update on Johnny Depp, Amber Heard, and the potential future of Warner Brothers.
snippet.description: I think these big companies are starting to underestimate their consumers. Johnny Depp gets paid in full for his involvement in Fantastic Beasts 3, petition to remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 reaches 1 million signatures, and Warner Brothers should think long and hard on whether or not they want to be associated with supporting spousal abuse.
